    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about keeping it spotless and well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready for you to just hop in and enjoy the ride. It\u2019s been so reliable and looks stunning in person. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
