    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccably preserved E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This example has undergone extensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS refresh with Beisan components. The chassis is structurally verified with documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring the integrity of the rear floor pan. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal lateral traction. The exterior retains its factory luster with consistent paint meter readings across all panels, while the interior features pristine Nappa leather with no bolster wear. A true mechanical masterpiece with zero deferred maintenance, ready for the most discerning collector.",
