    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, chips, or swirl marks, while the interior remains in a state of total preservation with supple, uncreased leather and pristine, factory-fresh carpeting. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates with the precision of a new vehicle. Meticulously maintained by a single owner and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage, it comes with a complete, documented service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example of automotive excellence that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
