      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered, garage-kept, and is basically spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one. Come see it for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
