      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera 4S represents a pinnacle of analog feedback and widebody aesthetics. The M96.03 3.6L flat-six engine has been fastidiously maintained, featuring a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a proactive rear main seal replacement to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag G96/31 six-speed manual transaxle, utilizing a viscous clutch all-wheel-drive system that remains flawlessly calibrated. The chassis is anchored by factory-spec Bilstein dampers and refreshed suspension bushings, eliminating any parasitic vibration or bushing deflection under high lateral G-loads. Braking performance is superlative, provided by four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors with zero heat checking. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with exceptional depth, while the cabin shows no signs of sun-fade or bolster compression. A true driver\u2019s specimen with zero mechanical deferred maintenance.",
